title: Ep41: New Year's Hoe-solutions
itunes:title: Ep41: New Year's Hoe-solutions
description:
We have reached the end of 2017. Can you believe it? In the last episode of the year, Mandii and Weezy skip down memory lane on previous episodes, favorite guests, and favorite moments. The two discuss which kinks they have conquered and which kinks they will save for 2018. The duo also share their 3 New Year's hoe-solutions and say what they would like to make change to in the coming year. This episode may be one of the funniest. Once again, thank you to our supporters! If you would like to support the podcast, become a patron at Patreon.com/whoreibledecisions and help us bring more content!!
